programme.desc: First up, Belgium is famous for its mussels and fries, aka 'Moule Frite'. The final dish is inspired by Belgian Waterzooi, a root veggie stew, mixed with a popular Malagesy stir-fry with shellfish and pork... programme.desc: Tiraditos!
